417
00:15:54.580 --> 00:15:55.780
Partamos juntos,

418
00:15:56.020 --> 00:15:57.300
he venido a proponértelo,

419
00:15:58.005 --> 00:15:59.765
tú y yo seremos malditos,

420
00:16:00.085 --> 00:16:01.205
